The stair-warden is a slab of black stone
with two brass keyholes cut into it.
$-- THE WARDEN OF THE ASCENT --
Three keys the master trusts to three
places. The blue of the armory. The red
of the sunken dead. The brass of the deep
keeper. Bring all three, or turn back.
!check;Present your keys.
!leave;Step back down the stair.
#end
:check
#play tc
#if bluekey blue_ok
The blue key is missing. The armory keeps
its own. Down you go, little climber.
#end
:blue_ok
#if redkey red_ok
The red key is missing. The crypt has not
yet given up its dead. Down you go.
#end
:red_ok
#if brasskey brass_ok
The brass key is missing. The deep keeper
still holds it. Down you go.
#end
:brass_ok
#play c+e+g+#c+f#c
