!wait;Stall and study the shadows
#end
:wait
#play tc-c
The Count merely smiles. Patience is a
luxury of the immortal, child. You have
perhaps four heartbeats of it left.
#zap wait
#send lord:touch
#end
:strike
#if havewater bless
#play f-f-f
You reach for a vial and find only dust.
The blessed water is still in the chapel.
His laughter fills the vaulted dark.
#end
